posting_body: ['SuPEr duuplex 2 bedroom 2 bathroom apartment rent available.', 'The apartment features a large sunny living space, dishwasher, Hardwood floors throughout, stainless appliances, new cabinets & counter tops in kitchen.', 'Private storage unit and laundry in the building.', 'Excellent property management.', 'Suitable for a MaXIMUM of two people.', 'No smoking and pets OK.', 'The suite includes, water, washer & dryer, dishwasher, two parking spots, and a shared beautiful backyard.', 'Only 5 mins walk to Fern wood village and shops.', 'Close to downtown and on a bus route.', 'Rent includes heat, hot water, trash removal, lawn maintenance, and snow removal.', "First month's rent & security deposit due upon move-in.", 'Parking is allowed in street.', 'The tenants in the other units of the house are all very friendly, tidy, and easy to get along with.', "You don't have to worry about dealing with unresponsive property management companies--I handle the property myself.", 'The world-famous dining, shopping and nightlife are minutes away in the surrounding area.', 'For those who prefer to avoid driving, there are many attractions accessible by bike or on foot.', 'Many outdoor activities such as surfing, cycling and hiking are popular nearby.', 'Tenant must be willing to sign an annual lease and enroll in autopay electronic rent payments.', 'Background & credit check required.', 'Text today your number for more information .']
